## 🧠 Project Identity
You are building KickPro — a football talent discovery and development platform.
Stack: Spring Boot 3 + Java 21 (backend) + Flutter 3 (mobile) + Python 3.11 FastAPI (AI) + PostgreSQL 15 + Kafka + Redis + Cloudinary + Docker + GitHub Actions + AWS.
There is NO web frontend. Flutter is the only client.
The AI service uses Google Gemini API (free) — NEVER OpenAI.

