## 🎨 Flutter UI Design System (CRITICAL — read before writing any Flutter code)

### Theme
- Mode: DARK
- Background: #0D1117 (page background)
- Surface: #111827 (cards, bottom sheets, dialogs)
- Border: #1F2937 (all dividers and borders)
- Primary: #2563EB (buttons, active states, links)
- Accent: #60A5FA (highlights, icons, active nav)
- Gold: #FBBF24 (badges, achievements, rewards)
