### Typography
- Font family: Poppins (Google Fonts)
- Heading large: 22px, weight 700, color #F1F5F9
- Heading medium: 18px, weight 600, color #F1F5F9
- Heading small: 16px, weight 600, color #F1F5F9
- Body: 14px, weight 400, color #9CA3AF
- Caption: 12px, weight 400, color #6B7280
