### UI Never Do
- No plain white backgrounds
- No generic Material blue (#1976D2)
- No flat boring list tiles
- No default AppBar — always custom
- No Lorem Ipsum — use realistic football data
- No static screens — always real dynamic data
- No default CircularProgressIndicator — use shimmer
